	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ah, zut.<10_4 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> Bah, certains n'aiment pas
